text: Eugenia Bokoka Mosua (born 3 June 2000), sportingly known as Anaís, is an Equatoguinean footballer who plays as a forward for Malabo Kings and the Equatorial Guinea women's national team. ==International career== Bokoka made her senior debut for Equatorial Guinea on 27 November 2017.
